				<div class="bookname">
					<h1>正文 第一百三十五章 自己决定命运！</h1>
					<div class="bottem1">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/uservote.php?id=602&amp;ajax_request=1');">投推荐票</a> <a href="/0_602/132297.html">上一章</a> ← <a href="http://www.booktxt.net/0_602/">章节目录</a> → <a href="/0_602/132299.html">下一章</a> <a href="javascript:;" onclick="showpop('/modules/article/addbookcase.php?id=602&amp;cid=132298&amp;ajax_request=1');">加入书签</a>
					</div>
					<div class="lm">&nbsp;热门推荐：<a href="/0_147/">天域苍穹</a>
				<a href="/0_316/" style="font-weight:bold">原始战记</a>
				<a href="/0_119/">雪鹰领主</a>
				<a href="/2_2219/">圣墟</a>
				<a href="/0_269/" style="font-weight:bold">总裁校花赖上我</a>
				<a href="/2_2270/">不朽凡人</a>
				<a href="/1_1227/" style="font-weight:bold">新大明帝国</a>
				<a href="/1_1411/">玄界之门</a>
				<a href="/1_1137/">一念永恒</a>
